  "keyFeatures": [
    "3-4x faster than MoviePy for common video editing tasks",
    "Numba JIT compilation for critical rendering operations",
    "Chainable API for intuitive video editing workflows",
    "Built-in visual effects (vfx), audio effects (afx), and transitions (vtx)",
    "Multiprocessing support for parallel rendering",
    "Frame-by-frame processing with full control",
    "Alpha channel and masking support",
    "Text rendering with pictex integration"
